    "description": "Your city is overrun with crime.<br>Underpaid and corrupt, the police are no match for the gangs.<br>Will you stand by and watch it burn, or will you take action?<br>Grab your weapon, customize it to your liking, and embark on a quest to reclaim your city.<br>Explore different locations plagued by criminal activity, eliminate threats, and gather clues to unlock new levels.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/d6980e49b8288dcdf5ef86a28db9762b.avif?t=1726938313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras_big/d6980e49b8288dcdf5ef86a28db9762b.avif?t=1726938313 width=800 height=48 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ONE HIT - ONE KILL</h2>But be careful—one bullet is all it takes to end your life or your enemies.<br>Watch your step.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/c180c414f7a49bbdc2b0f75e6d0cc034.poster.avif?t=1726938313\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/c180c414f7a49bbdc2b0f75e6d0cc034.webm?t=1726938313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/c180c414f7a49bbdc2b0f75e6d0cc034.mp4?t=1726938313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/d6980e49b8288dcdf5ef86a28db9762b.avif?t=1726938313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras_big/d6980e49b8288dcdf5ef86a28db9762b.avif?t=1726938313 width=800 height=48 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GAMEPLAY</h2>You start in your hideout where you can pick weapons and modify them.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/12de91787366f41b9c217487cf31058a.avif?t=1726938313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras_big/12de91787366f41b9c217487cf31058a.avif?t=1726938313 width=800 height=450 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/61540718fa064613c6d31e6b2d5fa890.poster.avif?t=1726938313\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/61540718fa064613c6d31e6b2d5fa890.webm?t=1726938313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/61540718fa064613c6d31e6b2d5fa890.mp4?t=1726938313\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/d6980e49b8288dcdf5ef86a28db9762b.avif?t=1726938313\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras_big/d6980e49b8288dcdf5ef86a28db9762b.avif?t=1726938313 width=800 height=48 /></span><br>Next go to the van which will take you to next location.<br>Your objective is to extract with at least one clue that you find on the map.<br>If succesfull You will unclock next level.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/13ca7dbc62f6beafdd6bcd4108bea3a7.poster.avif?t=1726938313\" width=720 height=480 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3207980/extras/13ca7dbc62f6beafdd6bcd4108bea3a7.webm?t=1726938313\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=